                  <persName id="t18161030-41-person408">
                  THOMAS 
                  HOBSON
               <interp inst="t18161030-41-person408" type="surname" value="HOBSON"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18161030-41-person408" type="given" value="THOMAS"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18161030-41-person408" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . On Wednesday evening the 25th of September, I was sitting in my parlour behind my shop, and the prisoner at the bar came in and went round the counter and pulled the till out. He must have seen me. I was coming out, and just as he got to the door, he have it down. When it was down, he took the money out and ran off, I went after him, and caught him just order the window. I did not know him before. I brought him him back into the shop, and sent for the watch. I I delivered him and the money to the watchman.</p>
               <p>GUILTY aged 12.</p>
